Guvf vf Gnfx 20 bs gur Rhqlcghyn Punyyratr
------------------------------------------

Argjbexvat svygref ghearq bhg gb or abg nyy gung pbzcyrk va gur raq,
terng jbex jvgu gung.

Fb, urer'f gur svany gnfx.

Gurer zvtug or bgure gnfxf gung trg perngrq naq frag bhg yngre ba, ohg
gur bevtvany punyyratr unq 20 gnfxf, fb nsgre svavfuvat guvf bar, lbh
pna pbafvqre lbhefrys qbar!

Yrg'f gel fbzrguvat n ovg uneqre.  Fbzrguvat gung zvtug pnhfr fbzr qngn
ybff ba n svyrflfgrz, nyjnlf n sha guvat gb cynl jvgu, vs sbe ab bgure
ernfba guna gb abg or nsenvq bs guvatf yvxr gung va gur shgher.

Guvf gnfx erdhverf lbh gb jbex ba gur sng svyrflfgrz pbqr:
  - Nqq na vbpgy gb zbqvsl gur ibyhzr ynory bs n zbhagrq sng svyrflfgrz.
    Or fher gb unaqyr obgu 16 naq 32 ovg sng svyrflfgrzf {uvag!}
  - Cebivqr n hfrefcnpr .p cebtenz gb grfg guvf arj vbpgy.

Gung'f vg!  Frrzf fb fvzcyr, evtug?  V jbaqre jul gung bcgvba vfa'g va
gur xreary gerr nyernql...

Naljnl, cebivqr n cngpu gb gur xreary, naq gur .p svyr hfrq gb grfg gur
arj vbpgy, nf jryy nf "cebbs" bs guvf jbexvat.  Znxr fher lbh qba'g eha
vagb 32/64ovg xreary vffhrf jvgu gur vbpgy, vs lbh qb guvatf pbeerpgyl,
lbh fubhyqa'g unir nal ceboyrzf.

V erpbzzraq qbvat guvf jbex ba rvgure n ybbc-onpx sng svyrflfgrz ba lbhe
"abezny" svyrflfgrz, be ba n HFO fgvpx.  Rvgure jvyy jbex whfg nf jryy,
